Class TetrominoData

    • Field Detail

      • parts

        public final Point[] parts
        This list specifies the parts of a tetromino, ie. the cells in its grid. Not all cells are used by the tetromino inside the rectangle of its bounding box, since each type of tetromino has different shape. This list includes only the used coordinates.

      • boundingBox

        public final Dimension boundingBox
        The bounding box specified by the tetromino's parts. Each cells are located inside this rectangle.
